com.codename1.webrtc

Interface Event

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RTCDTMFToneChangeEvent, RTCIdentityErrorEvent, RTCIdentityEvent, RTCPeerConnectionIceErrorEvent, RTCPeerConnectionIceEvent, RTCTrackEvent

    public interface Event

    The Event interface represents an event that takes place in the RTC instance. Any class that implements EventTarget may have EventListener objects registered that listen for events of a given type.

    See Also:
    https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event
